@startuml state-profile-lifecycle
title Child Profile Lifecycle

[*] --> Creating : Parent starts\nnew profile form

Creating : Name, age band,\navatar selected
Creating --> Active : Validation passes,\nprofile saved
Creating --> [*] : Parent cancels

Active : Profile visible\nin picker
Active --> Editing : Parent taps\nedit profile
Active --> Archived : Parent deletes\nprofile (soft-delete)

Editing : Name, age band, or\navatar being changed
Editing --> Active : Changes saved
Editing --> Active : Changes cancelled

Archived : Hidden from UI
Archived : Data retained per\nCOPPA requirements
Archived --> [*] : Retention period\nexpires (3 years)

@enduml
